race.comment: Competitive. I AM VOODOO (1) has been racing on the Poly and is bursting to win. Does have a decent record this course and distance and gets the big claim for the in-form apprentice. Drawn to box seat and expected to feature again. MIO SORRENTO (3) has been thereabouts lately including a close-up sixth at Eagle Farm latest. This looks ideal and gets a chance to find winning form. BENGAL DIAMOND (8) was racing in better races over the winter carnival in town. Fitter for two trials and has won fresh. Expecting a big return. PLATINUM LIES (7) has been thereabouts and looks the pace horse. Low draw, the claim and good speed will give a sight. MAGURO (2) has been at Eagle Farm the last couple and finds an easier assignment. Thornton is back aboard who is yet to miss the frame from five rides.
